Beautiful Planet Series 2 
This second instalment of the popular documentary series , Beautiful Planet is a superb series that shows the world at her best. It takes the viewer to unique nature locations throughout the world. Moreover the series explores the cultural highlights of the different countries. A must have for every nature and culture enthusiast!


1)  Disc 1 Belgium, Holland 
Disc 1 takes you to Belgium and the Netherlands. Bruges - the capital of West Flanders - with its impressive medieval city and the Dutch Kinderdijk windmill park with its unique are the goal.

